<a name="News" title="News"> </a>
<h2 class="underlined_10">News</h2>
<div class="section">
<a name="09+February+2009+-+Lucene+at+ApacheCon+Europe+2009+in+Amsterdam" title="09 February 2009 - Lucene at ApacheCon Europe 2009 in Amsterdam"> </a>
<h3 class="underlined_5">09 February 2009 - Lucene at ApacheCon Europe 2009 in Amsterdam</h3>
<div class="section">
<p>
          <a href="http://www.eu.apachecon.com/c/aceu2009/" title="ApacheCon EU 2009">
